bio.openEndedText: I'm a friendly, responsive, and flexible host.

Please feel free to call or text me at 563.650.0000 for any questions at all. 

Love cars, gone through 26 of them, in the past 5 years.  Currently drive a 2016 Maserati Ghibli S Sports Edition with beautiful, custom black with hand stitched red Interior, 2018 Tesla Model X with Falcon Wing doors, and Enhanced AutoPilot, and 2019 Tesla Model 3 Black on Black!

All my cars can be picked up in San Ramon at no charge. 

If you send me a request between midnight and 8am, I might not see it right away.  In that case, please cancel the request if you don't see a reply back from me within 15 mins, please call me.

Hello! My name is Amit and I'm an All-Star Turo Host with a response time of under 2 mins i.e. you can expect speedy responses throughout your trip. 

Your safety is my highest priority. During your trip, you can call 24/7 or text 650-402-2800.

Happy Driving!

Questions? Call/text me at any time of the day/night at (925) 858-7639

Focused on providing 5-Star service to all of my customers. 

Renting from me will be a breeze each and every time. Whether I am dropping a car off, or waiting for a pick up, the car will always be on time, clean, and ready to roll. Communication with my customers will always be a quick and clear response. 

Stay tuned as I will be adding to my fleet and continue providing exceptional service.

Hello, my name is Mat, and I run a technology consulting company throughout California.  Our all electric fleet of Tesla vehicles are available for any duration stays and offer unique features you won’t find in other listings. Try out Tesla’s FSD, or Acceleration Boost on one of our vehicles today! We offer 24x7 customer assistance and road side towing and service with every rental. Drive your dream Tesla today!

I am Sayed Juinda a hot star host at Turo I have over 10 years of experience in sales marketing and public relations, I am working with international students to get admitted into to their desired institutions in the US and Canada, career planning and help them start a new life in the US and Canada. Public relation is always been a passion for me and that’s why I started with Turo and wanted to explore my community and somehow help them overcome their transportation needs, my earnings are mostly going towards my Auto finance, insurances and maintenance a portion of the profit will support my family expenses I am a father of 3. I am originally from Afghanistan and landed in the US in 2017 such a fabulous country portion of my earnings is dedicated to charity for the ones who live back in my home country and need financial assistance. I hope every trip booked with us will be fun and hustle free - I am always here to support so talk to me if you feel anything while booking our cars. Thank you very much and God bless you all.
